---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro"
import SectionContainer from '../../components/blocks/SectionContainer.astro'
import SectionTitle from '../../components/blocks/SectionTitle.astro'

const writeups = await Astro.glob('./post/*.md')


---
<Layout>
<a href="./">BACK</a>
<SectionContainer>
    <SectionTitle title="Build A Saas"/>
    <div class="flex justify-evenly flex-col ">
        <p>
            This project is based on what I have learned through the past few years. I have dabbled in the full-stack, and I'm ready to share my work and thought process. 
        </p>
        <p>
            What has inspired me to build this saas project was inspired by a couple of things. First is the years I spent working in the validation group and how we tracked the countermeasure for the project.
            The second was understanding how bugs and other tasks were tracked in software. Seeing an opportunity to leverage the technology of the web to improve the performance of the group 
        </p>
        <div>
        Tech-stack: 
        <ul>
        <li>NEXT.js, A React Framework with hybrid static and server rendering</li>
        <li>Chakra.ui, modular and accessible component library that gives you the building blocks you need to build your React applications.</li>
        <li>Mock Service Worker (MSW), allowing a way to API mocking.</li>
        </ul>

        </div>
    </div>
</SectionContainer>


<div class="flex justify-center mb-10 font-extrabold text-xl">
<h2>Articles Pertaining to Saas</h2>

</div>

<ul class=" flex flex-col items-center">

{writeups.map(post=>{

        return(
            
            <div class="flex  flex-col m-4 w-7/12 p-4 bg-zinc-100 rounded">
                <div class="flex justify-between  my-3">
                    <a href={post.url}><h1 class="font-bold">{post.frontmatter.title}</h1></a>
                    <p class="font-light">{post.frontmatter.publishDate}</p>
                </div>
                <p class="px-4">{post.frontmatter.description}</p>
                <a class="underline m-4 self-end "href={post.url}>Read more</a>
            </div>
    )
})}

</ul>
</Layout>
